had a discussion

00:10:31.229 --> 00:10:32.520
about what the title should be.

00:10:32.520 --> 00:10:34.662
And we were like, I
think True Son is it.

00:10:34.662 --> 00:10:36.120
It started out as
the working title

00:10:36.120 --> 00:10:38.120
and then felt like it
really fit with the vision

00:10:38.120 --> 00:10:39.850
that we'd all been
thinking about.

