say go to as many
events as possible

00:12:34.244 --> 00:12:35.660
and meet as many
people as you can

00:12:35.660 --> 00:12:36.800
who don't work in
your department.

00:12:36.800 --> 00:12:38.900
I think that was the most
interesting thing for me,

00:12:38.900 --> 00:12:40.870
was really getting out and
meeting all the other interns

00:12:40.870 --> 00:12:42.390
and all the other
full-timers and just learning

00:12:42.390 --> 00:12:43.110
about what they do.

00:12:43.110 --> 00:12:45.400
Because everybody here has such
a unique and different role.

00:12:45.400 --> 00:12:47.524
And that was, I think, some
of the biggest learning

00:12:47.524 --> 00:12:49.340
opportunities for me
was just going to TGIF

00:12:49.340 --> 00:12:50.756
and sitting next
to someone random

00:12:50.756 --> 00:12:53.572
and just introducing myself and
learning about what they do.

00:12:53.572 --> 00:12:55.030
JHANVI SHRIRAM:
And I will probably

00:12:55.030 --> 00:12:56.090
