00:17:14.859 --> 00:17:16.170
So how do you do fund-raising?

00:17:16.170 --> 00:17:17.525
How do you do canvassing?

00:17:17.525 --> 00:17:18.900
How do you bring
people together?

00:17:18.900 --> 00:17:22.371
And so we've got these short
snippets on YouTube as well.

00:17:22.371 --> 00:17:23.579
MICHAEL TUBBS: So last thing.

00:17:23.579 --> 00:17:25.116
You're smart, so stay smart.

00:17:25.116 --> 00:17:27.490
Because no, seriously, because
oftentimes when people get

00:17:27.490 --> 00:17:29.160
elected they become dumb.

00:17:29.160 --> 00:17:31.730
Seriously, some of the things
they say just don't make sense.

00:17:31.730 --> 00:17:33.140
Did you read the staff report?

00:17:33.140 --> 00:17:34.872
So please just be smart.

00:17:34.872 --> 00:17:35.580
Do your homework.

00:17:35.580 --> 00:17:36.780
Do research.

00:17:36.780 --> 00:17:38.210
Let data guide your decisions.

00:17:38.210 --> 00:17:40.450
Because oftentimes people
make decisions off,

00:17:40.450 --> 00:17:42.080
back when I was
a kid this works.

00:17:42.080 --> 00:17:42.780
We're going to do this.

00:17:42.780 --> 00:17:43.750
What does the research say?

00:17:43.750 --> 00:17:45.166
A lot of people
don't do research.

