00:28:07.544 --> 00:28:09.335
MICHAEL TUBBS: Yeah
it's funny so last-- it

00:28:09.335 --> 00:28:10.835
was a couple
screenings ago, someone

00:28:10.835 --> 00:28:14.730
asked me, was it harder to
campaign or to be in office?

00:28:14.730 --> 00:28:15.740
