00:28:15.740 --> 00:28:16.730
I don't know.

00:28:16.730 --> 00:28:19.667
Campaigning was hard
because all day every day--

00:28:19.667 --> 00:28:22.000
but being in office is hard
because it's the same thing.

00:28:22.000 --> 00:28:23.830
And now I can't just
point my finger and say,

00:28:23.830 --> 00:28:24.670
this is what we should be doing.

