00:31:53.460 --> 00:31:55.070
Do they help you in office?

00:31:55.070 --> 00:31:57.750
So what is your relationship
like with youth today?

00:31:57.750 --> 00:31:59.333
MICHAEL TUBBS: It's
really interesting

00:31:59.333 --> 00:32:01.320
because now I'm old to people.

00:32:01.320 --> 00:32:02.140
So I teach.

00:32:02.140 --> 00:32:03.392
